txt.en: You have encountered a morvul stalker, a hidden and deadly foe, among the rest of the merrevail in the Circle of Madness.  There are surely others, and as long as they persist, they are a threat to the Rangers.
Morvul stalkers prowl the Circle of Madness, hidden from sight and extremely dangerous.
The morvul stalkers have been defeated, eliminating one more threat to the Rangers of Ithilien. You hope, but are somewhat certain they will not be, the last unseen enemy you face in the Morgul Vale.
Morvul stalkers are hidden somewhere in the Circle of Madness.\n\nYou should defeat morvul stalkers.
The morvul stalkers have been defeated, eliminating one more threat to the Rangers of Ithilien.
